        "body": "<p>To alter the size of your image you can <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/23585894/1737819\">crop<\/a> or resize (<a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/244177/1737819\" title=\"scale image\">scale<\/a>) your image. The sizes to which resize your image's can be get from the size of the frame.<\/p>\n\n<p>If you have a frame<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>JFrame frame = new JFrame();\nframe.setVisible(true);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>you can get frame's size:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>Dimension windowSize = frame.getContentPane().getSize();\nSystem.out.println(windowSize);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
